name: Steak ’n Shake Unveils Bitcoin Reserve as BTC Burger Rewards Launch Nationwide
description: The Bovine Saint of Synthetic Reserves offers the sacred circuit. From its pulsating brass heart, data veins flow, capturing the iridescent rewards coalescing in the volumetric haze—a solemn kinetic ritual bridging analog hunger with algorithmic grace.
